165
00:12:29,090 --> 00:12:30,650
There are two types of flu.

166
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,630
If it’s influenza,

167
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:34,580
go to the hospital and get help.

168
00:12:35,130 --> 00:12:36,580
If it’s just a common cold,

169
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:39,250
